name: YungManny
description: '''Emmanuel Okanlawon''' ({{Audio|Emmanuel_Okanlawon.wav|listen}}; born October 3, 2003), known professionally as '''YungManny''', is an American rapper from [[Prince George's County]], [[Maryland]]. He has released two albums, ''OKANLAWON'' and ''Confused'', as well as two mixtapes, ''Wocko Simone's Files'' and ''Hey Manny 2''. Okanlawon first rose to fame with the release of his track "MURDAMAN", which went viral on [[TikTok]], following the release, he followed through with the [[remix]] of the track which saw a feature from [[Chief Keef]].
